* Iron Raptor watched Quake transform into his beast mode, stepping back as 
he began to shuffle around.
She wasn't quite sure of this now, he was a bit big and...basically seemed 
to cover the floor.
She pressed herself against the wall as his tail slithered past, looking at 
him but keeping her cool.
She sighed and brought up a digital map in the center of the table, the pic 
of the Ark the way it was now showing up.*

" Is this what you're looking for?"
